geographicalLocations: 1201 Taylor St - San Fran. Cal - Mrs C. H. Rye - Oregon City
fullText: This was thrown out - because of my accepting Mrs Cummings Congress on June 8.9.10 - so could not make two such long trips went again to Dentist this A.M.
summaryText: Susan B. Anthony's plans were cancelled due to a previous commitment and she went to the dentist.
